# Netlify Redirects for TaxFlow Enhanced
# This file provides a backup to netlify.toml redirects configuration

# SPA Fallback - redirect all routes to index.html
# This ensures React Router handles all routing client-side
/*    /index.html   200

# Optional: Redirect www to non-www (uncomment if needed)
# https://www.taxflow.example.com/*  https://taxflow.example.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: Redirect non-www to www (uncomment if needed)
# https://taxflow.example.com/*  https://www.taxflow.example.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: Force HTTPS (Netlify does this automatically, but you can be explicit)
# http://taxflow.example.com/*  https://taxflow.example.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: Custom 404 page (if you create one)
# /404  /index.html  404
